*Shadow Cat and Snow Tech dodge through the passing trees, trying to keep 
the smaller bot in their sites. After losing him once, they did not want to 
lose him a second time, after all, he was valuable.
the little critter zipped and dogged trees and rocks, losing them behind a 
large stand of trees and bushes.*

" damn, i can't see him Shad. I really don't want to lose him!"

*Snow Tech says, then, relizing that he had just addmited to his sister that 
he liked the little fuzz-ball of cuteness, he stammered an exscuse,*

" Uh, i mean, after all. chicks dig guys with cute kids with them!"

* SHadow Cat just grinned and shot ahead and through the trees, almost 
running into Iron Raptor and the fuzz-ball. Suprised, Shadow Cat came to 
emergancy stop, putting on her brakes as hard as possible*

" Iron? What the.....? How'd you get here? After me'n Snowy left i thought 
i'de never see you again! After all, it's been years....."

* In her suprise and confusion, she did not warn Snow Tech that she had 
stopped, making the large cat-bot to promptely run into her, leaving them in 
tangled mess.*





love, Shadow Cat and Snow Tech

                        A.J.
